data.title: Athletic Bilbao beats Mallorca on penalties to win first Copa del Rey in 40 years
data.meta_description: Athletic Bilbao beat Mallorca 4-2 on penalties to end a 40-year wait for its 24th Copa del Rey title on Saturday.
